        <updateDate>2021-06-23T17:08:00Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Vaccines for Emergencies Act of 2021 or the SAVE Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the President to make payments to manufacturers to increase supply-chain security if doing so is important to the national defense. </p> <p>The President must submit a strategy to Congress that includes (1) a plan to use authorities under the Defense Production Act of 1950 to ensure the supply of medical materials essential to the national defense; and (2) plans to diversify, and address vulnerabilities in, supply chains for essential medical materials.</p> <p>The President must submit to Congress annual progress reports through FY2025 evaluating the implementation of the strategy.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>53</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-05-18</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-06-23T18:22:49Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Vaccines for Emergencies Act of 2021 or the SAVE Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the President to make payments to manufacturers to increase supply-chain security if doing so is important to the national defense. </p> <p>The President must submit a strategy to Congress that includes (1) a plan to use authorities under the Defense Production Act of 1950 to ensure the supply of medical materials essential to the national defense; and (2) plans to diversify, and address vulnerabilities in, supply chains for essential medical materials.</p> <p>The President must submit to Congress annual progress reports through FY2025 evaluating the implementation of the strategy.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
